OL,3,CPolice probe attempted murder
OL,4,Cfollowing hit-and-run in Dumfries
OL,6,FPolice in Dumfries and Galloway are
OL,7,Fappealing for information following a
OL,8,Fhit-and-run attempted murder.
OL,10,FThe incident happened shortly after
OL,11,F11pm on Saturday 17th May.
OL,13,FPolice Scotland say a man was hit by a
OL,14,Fcar on Criffel Road and that the
OL,15,Fvehicle and its occupants left the
OL,16,Fscene in the direction of College Road
OL,17,Fand Newbridge Drive.
OL,19,FA 28-year-old man was taken to
OL,20,FDumfries and Galloway Royal Infirmary
OL,21,Fwith serious injuries.
