OL,6,FOfficers say enquiries have
OL,7,Festablished that a silver VW Golf was
OL,8,Fin the area at the time.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Scott Wilson said:
OL,11,F"Extensive enquiries are ongoing and
OL,12,Fwe have been gathering CCTV footage
OL,13,Ffrom the surrounding area, which is
OL,14,Fbeing reviewed.
OL,16,F"Officers have also been carrying out
OL,17,Fdoor to door enquiries in the local
OL,18,Farea and will continue to do so.
