OL,6,F"But I would also be very keen to
OL,7,Fspeak anyone who was in the area at
OL,8,Fthe time or has seen the car since
OL,9,Fthen and may be able to assist our
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,F"I would also like to hear from anyone
OL,13,Fwho has dash cam, private CCTV or
OL,14,Fdoorbell footage from the Lincluden
OL,15,Farea around the time of the incident.
OL,17,F"Any information, or footage, could
OL,18,Fprove vital, so please do pass it on
OL,19,Fto officers.
